      <title>澳大利亚公布大选前预算中的惊喜减税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/australia-unveils-surprise-tax-cuts-in-pre-election-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚的左翼政府在大选前预算中揭示了意外的减税和能源回扣的扩展，旨在抚养选民的生活成本，并帮助确保总理安东尼·阿尔巴尼斯（Anthony Albanese）任期第二任期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/australia-unveils-surprise-tax-cuts-in-pre-election-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 08:32:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚2025联邦预算：谁是获奖者和失败者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/australia-2025-federal-budget-who-were-the-winners-and-losers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当澳大利亚人准备参加民意测验时，政府推出了其2025  -  26年的联邦预算，该预算有望为所有纳税人提供进一步的救济，并为有孩子的儿童幼儿教育，学生债务持有人和啤酒饮酒者提供一些激励措施。这是财务主管吉姆·查尔默斯（Jim Chalmers）的大选前财政蓝图中的一些获奖者和失败者的细分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/australia-2025-federal-budget-who-were-the-winners-and-losers</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 08:32:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰，美国团队据说将在沙特阿拉伯举行更多会谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/ukraine-us-teams-said-to-be-holding-more-talks-in-saudi-arabia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位了解此事的人说，乌克兰和美国团队在利雅得举行了另一轮谈判，讨论了30天的能源和俄罗斯战争中的黑海停火。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/ukraine-us-teams-said-to-be-holding-more-talks-in-saudi-arabia</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 08:19:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>劳动力废料每年20亿英镑的移民酒店合同</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/labour-scraps-2-billion-a-year-migrant-hotels-contract</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府正在与一家公司与一家公司提供20亿英镑（26亿美元）的合同，该公司以对其绩效和行为的不明确担忧提供了该国约四分之一的住宿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/labour-scraps-2-billion-a-year-migrant-hotels-contract</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 07:50:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普华永道对古普塔（Gupta）的Wyelands银行的审计，由英国监管机构审核</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/pwc-fined-over-audit-of-gupta-s-wyelands-bank-by-uk-watchdog</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家英国监管机构罚款PriceWaterhouseCoopers LLP及其会计师之一，因为他们对Sanjeev Gupta的Wyelands Bank的有缺陷的审计，此前贸易财务专家Greenensill Capital崩溃了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/pwc-fined-over-audit-of-gupta-s-wyelands-bank-by-uk-watchdog</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 07:41:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本的Ishiba计划价格措施通过现有预算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/ishiba-plans-powerful-inflation-measures-ahead-of-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本总理Shigeru Ishiba正在计划采取措施，以减轻通货膨胀对消费者的影响，这些消费者利用已经在当前和即将到来的会计年度预算中纳入的政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/ishiba-plans-powerful-inflation-measures-ahead-of-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 06:44:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
